title: 'It is possible to use record update syntax to update dependent fields, provided that all related fields are updated at once. For example:'
pid: a9756b8a-f1ac-48fe-a606-65cb9cf08da1
body: |2-
  cons : t -> (x : Nat ** Vect x t) -> (x : Nat ** Vect x t)
  cons val xs
      = { fst := S (fst xs),
          snd := (val :: snd xs) } xs
  Or even:

  cons' : t -> (x : Nat ** Vect x t) -> (x : Nat ** Vect x t)
  cons' val
      = { fst $= S,
          snd $= (val ::) }
